<section xml:id="sec-chromatic-button-accordion-intro">
    <title>A Chromatic Button Accordion</title>
    <p>
        The chromatic button accordion is a versatile instrument, distinguished by its button-based keyboard layout and rich tonal possibilities. This section provides an overview of a C system instrument with Stradella and Free Bass systems.
    </p>
<figure width="100\%" xml:id="master-58-b-de-luxe"> 
<caption>High quality Italian Chromatic Button Accordion with Stradella and Free Bass.</caption>

    <image source="master-58-b-de-luxe.jpg">

    <shortdescription>High Quality Italian Chromatic Button Accordion with Free Bass and Stradella. The treble side keyboard is configured in the C System. </shortdescription>
    </image>
 </figure>


</section>
